---
// Concept 3 — Viselli-inspired intro: clean, restrained, one short statement
---

<section id="c3-manifesto" class="c3-mfst">
  <div class="c3-mfst-inner">

    <p class="c3-mfst-label" data-reveal>New Zealand · Australia</p>

    <h2 class="c3-mfst-statement" data-reveal data-delay="100">
      We don't plan trips.<br />We reveal places.
    </h2>

    <div class="c3-mfst-body-wrap" data-reveal data-delay="200">
      <p class="c3-mfst-body">
        Private itineraries crafted for travellers who know that the finest
        experiences are never found in a brochure — they are uncovered through
        quiet access, deep relationships, and a genuine love of these lands.
      </p>
      <a href="/about" class="c3-mfst-link">
        Our approach
        <svg width="12" height="8" viewBox="0 0 14 10" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
          <path d="M9 1l4 4-4 4M13 5H1" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1"/>
        </svg>
      </a>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .c3-mfst {
    background: #F5F0E9;
    padding: clamp(72px, 10vw, 140px) clamp(24px, 6vw, 100px);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(17, 34, 80, 0.07);
  }
  .c3-mfst-inner {
    max-width: 1320px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 200px 1fr 1fr;
    gap: clamp(32px, 5vw, 80px);
    align-items: start;
  }
  .c3-mfst-label {
    font-family: 'Lato', sans-serif;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-style: italic;
    letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    color: rgba(17, 34, 80, 0.4);
    padding-top: 8px;
    margin: 0;
  }
  .c3-mfst-statement {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: clamp(28px, 3.5vw, 48px);
    font-weight: 300;
    font-style: italic;
    color: #112250;
    line-height: 1.18;
    margin: 0;
    letter-spacing: 0.01em;
  }
  .c3-mfst-body-wrap {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 28px;
    padding-top: 6px;
  }
  .c3-mfst-body {
    font-family: 'Lato', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(13px, 1.1vw, 15px);
    font-style: italic;
    color: rgba(17, 34, 80, 0.58);
    line-height: 1.95;
    margin: 0;
  }
  .c3-mfst-link {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    font-family: 'Lato', sans-serif;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-style: italic;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    color: #112250;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(17, 34, 80, 0.25);
    padding-bottom: 3px;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: gap 0.3s ease, border-color 0.3s ease;
  }
  .c3-mfst-link:hover {
    gap: 16px;
    border-color: rgba(17, 34, 80, 0.7);
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .c3-mfst-inner {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 28px;
    }
  }
</style>
